These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-1::.
City: rome, new-york, miami
1. the person traveling to miami is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |   3    |
| City   | rome | new-york | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-2::.
City: liverpool, hannover, boston
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to boston is in the middle##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |   2   |   3   |
| City   | liverpool | boston | hannover |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, tennis, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Sport   | tennis | cricket | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, milk
1. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, davidoff, cain
1. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |   3    |
| Cigar   | bolivar | davidoff | cain |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Hobby   | traveling | filmmaking | writing |

