.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, ice-hockey, rowing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is parkour##2
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | rowing | parkour |

